<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">1940 Lamp controller (01PBA03) firmware update failed</b> </title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-B87BF88B-91B2-4C27-A55C-91B9B6986C8A"><p class="- topic/p "> 1940 The firmware update of the Lamp controller (01PBA03) has failed. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">This can happen when the e.g. top cover is opened during firmware upgrade since the curing components are interlocked by the top cover. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">During the next start up, the firmware update is retried again. If it keeps failing (without opening covers) the lamp controller needs to be replaced 
</p><note class="- topic/note " id="GUID-8F2BED33-7018-400B-8452-88C80DEB830C"><p class="- topic/p "> Retry the upgrade minimum 3 times. If it keeps failing, replace the Lamp controller. 
</p></note><p class="- topic/p "> You can temporarily disable the firmware update by means of parameter 
<xref class="- topic/xref " keyref="SDS01-1-035" href="GUID-D2778EAF-24DE-41F5-8EEE-BCB7BCCBAB96.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text xref?>01-1-035 Enable firmware update of curing components [Parameters]</xref>. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The printer can usually be used with the current firmware. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">After replacing the UV lamp controller the parameter<xref class="- topic/xref " keyref="SDS01-1-035" href="GUID-D2778EAF-24DE-41F5-8EEE-BCB7BCCBAB96.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text xref?>01-1-035 Enable firmware update of curing components [Parameters]</xref> needs to be set to 1 again. 
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Diagnostics</category></metadata></prolog><tsBody class="- topic/body tsTroubleshooting/tsBody "><tsSymptoms id="GUID-33E1B64A-E818-4500-A780-C8BC692D14B2" class="- topic/section tsTroubleshooting/tsSymptoms "/><tsCauses id="GUID-015BBB51-2D3A-46CB-B0D3-63A93989FCAC" class="- topic/section tsTroubleshooting/tsCauses "><p class="- topic/p "> <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Lamp control PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 01PBA03 </compcodenr></comp> 
</p></tsCauses><tsDiagnose id="GUID-D26BEC88-1842-4144-AC15-A1A4DD8B2FC8" class="- topic/section tsTroubleshooting/tsDiagnose "><p class="- topic/p ">Check / replace the <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Lamp control PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 01PBA03 </compcodenr></comp> 
